metadata.name: Culture Cartel Genesis #1
metadata.description:
Launched in 2018 as a venue and platform for street artists, designers, tattoo artists and urban brands across the world to gather and display their craft, Culture Cartel aims to curate a holistic, educational and engaging street culture showcase that has never been seen before in Asia; further cementing Singapore as a regional street culture hub.

The Culture Cartel Genesis NFT collection will push the boundaries of web3 culture, equipped with utilities like VIP access to events, giveaways and raffle draws of coveted limited-edition merchandise from leading brands and artists.
